Package: seminrExtras
Type: Package
Title: Conduct Additional Modeling and Analysis for 'seminr'
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(person("Soumya", "Ray", email = "soumya.ray@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "ths")),
             person("Nicholas Patrick", "Danks", email = "nicholasdanks@hotmail.com", role = c("aut","cre"))
            )
Description: Supplemental functions for estimating and analysing structural equation models.
    Methods include Cross Validated Predictive Ability Testing (CVPAT, Liengaard et al., 2021 <doi:10.1111/deci.12445>),
    Predictive Contribution of the Mediator (PCM, Danks, 2021 <doi:10.1145/3505639.3505644>),
    Combined Importance-Performance Map Analysis (cIPMA, Sarstedt et al., 2024
    <doi:10.1057/s41270-023-00275-x>; Hauff et al., 2024 <doi:10.1016/j.jretconser.2024.103723>),
    Composite Overfit Analysis (COA), Necessary Condition Analysis (NCA, Dul, 2016 <doi:10.1177/1094428116689707>)
    with the Effect Size Sensitivity Extension (NCA-ESSE, Becker et al., 2026
    <doi:10.1016/j.jbusres.2025.115920>), Confirmatory Tetrad Analysis (CTA-PLS,
    Gudergan et al., 2008 <doi:10.1016/j.jbusres.2008.01.012>), Prediction-Oriented
    Segmentation (PLS-POS, Becker et al., 2013 <doi:10.25300/MISQ/2013/37.3.02>),
    and congruence coefficient testing.
Imports:
    seminr (>= 2.4.0),
    stats,
    graphics,
    grDevices,
    utils,
    rpart
